text: Measure for sample 3 OCP then CV then OCP and then CA.
Measure OCP for all samples and for the sample with the highest OCP also perform CV and CA.
Measure CV for all samples and place them to user area.
The sequence is OCP then CV then CA. Measure for all samples the sequence.
Run CA for all samples and for the sample with the lowest current density also OCP followed by CV.
